(13, 1, NULL, '2013-02-28', 'Berry Muffins', 'berry-muffins', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>fb kafgklfsdauufkl sdakbefbsdlasafysaysjkvsjk vjgak blsadb</p>', NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 28, '10 mins', '17 mins', '12', '<p>These easy to make muffins are packed full of healthy blueberries and blackberries and make a great standby for a quick breakfast, lunchbox addition or coffee time treat.</p>', 44, 43),
(14, 1, NULL, '2013-03-07', 'Apple-pecan Muffins With Salted Caramel Pecans', 'Apple-pecan-muffins', 99, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>fb kafgklfsdauufkl sdakbefbsdlasafysaysjkvsjk vjgak blsadb</p>', NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 15, '25 MINS', '17 MINS', '12', '<p class="p1">These muffins are a lovely marriage of flavours with light, moist muscovado cane sugar, cinnamon and sweet apples.</p>', 149, 148),
(15, 1, NULL, '2013-03-07', 'Affogato Al Caffe', 'affogato-al-caffe', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 14, '5 MINS', 'NONE', '4', '<p>This coffee based drink-come-dessert is highly delicious and oh-so-easy to make. It&rsquo;s just a shot of hot espresso poured over a scoop of vanilla ice cream and sprinkled with glistening Demerara for some crunchiness. Serve with a crisp biscuit, and customise with your favourite liqueur, if you wish.</p>', 151, 150),
(16, 1, NULL, '2013-03-07', 'Bread & Butter Pudding', 'bread-butter-pudding', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 13, '20 MINS', '30 MINS', '4', '<p>The addition of a vanilla pod and orange zest, along with the subtle sweetness of the luscious golden syrup cane sugar, transforms the humble bread and butter pudding into something quite special.</p>', 153, 152),
(17, 1, 184, '2013-03-07', 'Caramel Popcorn', 'caramel-popcorn', 8, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Popping with taste</p>', NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 17, '10 MINS', '15 MINS', '6', '<p>This caramel popcorn is a real Saturday night TV treat for all the family. If you&rsquo;re making it ahead of time store in an airtight container so that it retains its crunchiness.</p>', 155, 154),
(18, 1, NULL, '2013-03-07', 'Caramelised Blueberry Tart', 'caramelised-blueberry-tart', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 12, '30 MINS', '45-50 MINS', '6-8', '<p>The brittle cane sugared top on this purple-juiced blueberry tart is a perfect contrast to the softly set cinnamon custard.</p>', 157, 156),
(19, 1, NULL, '2013-03-11', 'Carrot and Walnut Cake', 'carrot-and-walnut-cake', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 13, '1 hour', '55-60 mins', '8', '<p>An adaptation of Ottolenghi&rsquo;s recipe, this is a light, moist and sublime cake with a rich, citrus icing and crunchy caramelised walnuts.</p>', 234, 233),
(20, 1, NULL, '2013-03-11', 'Chocolate Swirl Meringues', 'chocolate-swirl-meringues', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 11, '20 mins', '2 hours', '10', '<p>These large, indulgent clouds of chewy chocolate meringues taste as gorgeous as they look.</p>', 236, 235),
(21, 1, NULL, '2013-03-11', 'Chocolate Mocha Brownies', 'chocolate-mocha-brownies', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 15, '25 mins', '25 mins', '16', '<p>Rich and gooey, these brownies hit the spot when you want an indulgent chocolate fix. Serve on their own with ice cream, or cut into tiny squares for serving with after dinner coffee.</p>', 238, 237),
(22, 1, NULL, '2013-03-11', 'Churros with Cinnamon Sugar', 'churros-with-cinnamon-sugar', 99, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'recipe_article', 11, '15 mins', '25 mins', '30', '<p>Churros, sweet fried choux pastry fritters, liberally dusted with cane sugar, are a Spanish institution typically served at breakfast with hot chocolate for dipping. With or without hot chocolate they are absolutely divine.</p>', 241, 240),
